        <div class="eb-article__headline-wrapper">
            <h1 id="ebStoryHeadline" class="eb-article__headline" data-eb-story-headline="Explaining the Philippines’ ‘writ of kalikasan’: What does the special legal remedy mean for nature protection?">
                Explaining the Philippines’ ‘writ of kalikasan’: What does the special legal remedy mean for nature protection?
            </h1>
        </div>

        <div class="eb-article__standfirst-wrapper">
            
                <h2 class="eb-article__standfirst">A most recent case involves the Supreme Court issuing the nature writ to stop mining firms from operating in Palawan. Eco-Business looks into this unique mechanism under Philippine environmental law that gives the people constitutional right to a healthy&nbsp;environment.</h2>
            
        </div>
        

        
            <div class="eb-article__media">
                
                    
                        <figure class="eb-article__featured-image">
                            
